The paper deals with image and video processing, specifically super-resolution of color and depth images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of 3D videos, which suggests a possible connection to graphics (cs.GR). The use of neural networks and loss functions indicates a possible connection to machine learning (cs.MM, cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes a novel approach to solving the problem, which suggests a possible connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
